p-text.children: The Taycan thrills within fractions of a second: with a fluid yet sharp silhouette and a dynamic fly line. Seen enough? Definitely not.
Launch control can be activated in both Sport and Sport Plus mode, prepares all systems for maximum acceleration, and delivers incredible power to the tarmac.

For dynamic driving, the Taycan is fitted with the Porsche Active Aerodynamics system with active cool air intakes and an adaptive, triple-level rear spoiler. At 90 km/h, 160 km/h and 200 km/h, it transforms an electric vehicle into a sports car with Porsche DNA.

Mechanical buttons have been almost entirely replaced by digital ones. Making the cockpit look extremely tidy. The innovative curved display is always right in front of you. It offers state-of-the-art comfort for an electrifying driving experience.

p-headline.children: For those who want even more. The Taycan GTS.

p-text.children: The Taycan GTS embodies pure dynamics. A GTS-specific drive for increased agility and the typical GTS sound with a robust soundscape make the vehicle unmistakable – and every time you want more.

Black lettering on the rear, sideskirts with black inlays and the SportDesign upper front section sharpen the sporty look of the Taycan GTS. The vehicle can also be refined with carbon elements from the optional SportDesign Carbon package.

The adaptive air suspension with GTS-specific setup and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) brings even more stability. Depending on the road surface and driving style, the damping force of the shock absorbers is electronically adjusted and comfort is increased on all seats.
